com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport
Class CardProvenance

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport.CardProvenance

public final class CardProvenance
extends Object

The provenance of the data on a Card that an Item in the Intelligence Analysis Platform contains.

Provenance enables the Intelligence Analysis Platform to determine whether two pieces of data have the same origin, and to retrieve data from an external source some time after it was first stored on a Card.

Since:
4.0
